    <string name="help_para_1">Welcome to MagnetArt! This app offers a unique drawing experience. MagnetArt is designed to be used a cylindrical or disc magnet. Place the phone or tablet on a flat surface next to the area where you wish to draw. To create a new drawing press the plus button on the home screen.</string>
    <string name="help_para_2">A dialog will be shown as the device calculates the background magnetic field. When this dialog disappears, place the magnet in a corner of the drawing area and press the button to calibrate that corner. Each button will turn green when calibrated.</string>
    <string name="help_para_3">Repeat this for all four corners. When all four corners have been calibrated you are ready to begin drawing. The drawing shapes can be chosen using the menu. The default shape is a spot drawn at the magnet position.</string>
    <string name="help_para_4">The corners of the triangle or rectangle are drawn when a finger is placed onscreen. Place a finger onscreen and move the magnet to draw a side. To draw a circle place a finger onscreen and move the magnet to determine the radius.</string>
    <string name="help_para_5">The stroke colour and background colour can also be changed using the menu. When the colour bar is shown, move the magnet to select a colour and press confirm.</string>
    <string name="help_para_6">To save a drawing, either press save on the menu or press your device back button. Confirm you wish to save. You can view your saved drawings when you return to the app home screen. You can scroll through your saved drawings and click on a drawing to view it. To delete an image press the bin icon and confirm.</string>
